{"title":"American Chopper x Ruff Cycles leads EB21 e-bike cafe cruiser roundup","link":"https://bikerumor.com/2021/09/04/american-chopper-x-ruff-cycles-leads-eb21-e-bike-cafe-cruiser-roundup/","date":1630766268000,"content":"<div id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"><div role=\"main\"><article id=\"post-270485\" role=\"article\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/BlogPosting\"><section itemprop=\"text\"><p>We always knew e-bikes were going to be a trend at Eurobike this year, but a collaboration with Paul Jr. Designs of American Chopper fame made clear that chopper &amp; cafe cruiser motorcycle designs would inspire a growing crop of e-bikes to cruise around town. While we’ve seen a number e-cruisers before – even several throttle-based e-motos – this latest crop takes advantage of pretty much every style of pedal-assist e-bike powertrain on the market. Check out the latest &amp; greatest we spotted from Ruff Cycles, Aevon Bikes, Super73 &amp; Rayvolt…</p><h2>Paul Jr. Designs X Ruff Cycles <em>American Chopper</em>-inspired e-bike cruiser</h2><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/04094237/Paul-Jr-Designs-X-Ruff-Cycles-American-Chopper-e-bike_cruiser-detail.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/04094237/Paul-Jr-Designs-X-Ruff-Cycles-American-Chopper-e-bike_cruiser-detail.jpg\" alt=\"Paul Jr. Designs X Ruff Cycles American Chopper e-bike cruiser\" width=\"1600\" height=\"1200\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/04094237/Paul-Jr-Designs-X-Ruff-Cycles-American-Chopper-e-bike_cruiser-detail.jpg 1600w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/04094237/Paul-Jr-Designs-X-Ruff-Cycles-American-Chopper-e-bike_cruiser-detail-297x223.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/04094237/Paul-Jr-Designs-X-Ruff-Cycles-American-Chopper-e-bike_cruiser-detail-800x600.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/04094237/Paul-Jr-Designs-X-Ruff-Cycles-American-Chopper-e-bike_cruiser-detail-120x90.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/04094237/Paul-Jr-Designs-X-Ruff-Cycles-American-Chopper-e-bike_cruiser-detail-768x576.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/04094237/Paul-Jr-Designs-X-Ruff-Cycles-American-Chopper-e-bike_cruiser-detail-1536x1152.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb28 src ng ngcb28 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/04094237/Paul-Jr-Designs-X-Ruff-Cycles-American-Chopper-e-bike_cruiser-detail.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/04094237/Paul-Jr-Designs-X-Ruff-Cycles-American-Chopper-e-bike_cruiser-detail.jpg 1600w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/04094237/Paul-Jr-Designs-X-Ruff-Cycles-American-Chopper-e-bike_cruiser-detail-297x223.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/04094237/Paul-Jr-Designs-X-Ruff-Cycles-American-Chopper-e-bike_cruiser-detail-800x600.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/04094237/Paul-Jr-Designs-X-Ruff-Cycles-American-Chopper-e-bike_cruiser-detail-120x90.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/04094237/Paul-Jr-Designs-X-Ruff-Cycles-American-Chopper-e-bike_cruiser-detail-768x576.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/04094237/Paul-Jr-Designs-X-Ruff-Cycles-American-Chopper-e-bike_cruiser-detail-1536x1152.jpg 1536w\"></a></p><p>The PJD-E Ruffian, a limited edition e-bike cruiser made by Ruff Cycles in Europe, was designed by custom motorcycle designer Paul Teutul Jr of <em>American Chopper</em> fame, said to be inspired by his motorcycle from their “Build-Off 2” custom challenge. The e-bike is built by Ruff with an aluminum frameset crafted in Bosnia and Herzegovina before heading to their German HQ for getting finished off by hand.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/04094241/Paul-Jr-Designs-X-Ruff-Cycles-American-Chopper-e-bike_cruiser-non-driveside.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/04094241/Paul-Jr-Designs-X-Ruff-Cycles-American-Chopper-e-bike_cruiser-non-driveside.jpg\" alt=\"Paul Jr. Designs X Ruff Cycles American Chopper e-bike cruiser\" width=\"1600\" height=\"900\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/04094241/Paul-Jr-Designs-X-Ruff-Cycles-American-Chopper-e-bike_cruiser-non-driveside.jpg 1600w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/04094241/Paul-Jr-Designs-X-Ruff-Cycles-American-Chopper-e-bike_cruiser-non-driveside-297x167.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/04094241/Paul-Jr-Designs-X-Ruff-Cycles-American-Chopper-e-bike_cruiser-non-driveside-800x450.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/04094241/Paul-Jr-Designs-X-Ruff-Cycles-American-Chopper-e-bike_cruiser-non-driveside-120x68.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/04094241/Paul-Jr-Designs-X-Ruff-Cycles-American-Chopper-e-bike_cruiser-non-driveside-768x432.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/04094241/Paul-Jr-Designs-X-Ruff-Cycles-American-Chopper-e-bike_cruiser-non-driveside-1536x864.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb28 src ng ngcb28 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/04094241/Paul-Jr-Designs-X-Ruff-Cycles-American-Chopper-e-bike_cruiser-non-driveside.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/04094241/Paul-Jr-Designs-X-Ruff-Cycles-American-Chopper-e-bike_cruiser-non-driveside.jpg 1600w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/04094241/Paul-Jr-Designs-X-Ruff-Cycles-American-Chopper-e-bike_cruiser-non-driveside-297x167.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/04094241/Paul-Jr-Designs-X-Ruff-Cycles-American-Chopper-e-bike_cruiser-non-driveside-800x450.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/04094241/Paul-Jr-Designs-X-Ruff-Cycles-American-Chopper-e-bike_cruiser-non-driveside-120x68.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/04094241/Paul-Jr-Designs-X-Ruff-Cycles-American-Chopper-e-bike_cruiser-non-driveside-768x432.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/04094241/Paul-Jr-Designs-X-Ruff-Cycles-American-Chopper-e-bike_cruiser-non-driveside-1536x864.jpg 1536w\"></a></p><p>The 25km/hr pedal-assist e-bike is being offered in Europe only for the time being for 6600€. It is powered by a Bosch Performance Line CX motor with a 500W battery hidden in the chopper’s tank, an Enviolo CVT hub out back for a wide gearing range through a Gates belt drive, and Magura hydraulic disc brakes.</p><p><a href=\"https://www.ruff-cycles.com/pauljrdesigns\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><em>Ruff-cycles.com/PaulJrDesigns</em></a></p><h3>Ruff Cycles Biggie cafe racer e-bike cruiser</h3><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/04091723/Ruff-Cycles-Biggie-e-bike_Bosch-mid-motor-cafe-racer-cruiser-with-bags.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/04091723/Ruff-Cycles-Biggie-e-bike_Bosch-mid-motor-cafe-racer-cruiser-with-bags.jpg\" alt=\"Ruff Cycles Biggie cafe racer e-bike cruiser\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1200\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/04091723/Ruff-Cycles-Biggie-e-bike_Bosch-mid-motor-cafe-racer-cruiser-with-bags.jpg 1500w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/04091723/Ruff-Cycles-Biggie-e-bike_Bosch-mid-motor-cafe-racer-cruiser-with-bags-297x238.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/04091723/Ruff-Cycles-Biggie-e-bike_Bosch-mid-motor-cafe-racer-cruiser-with-bags-800x640.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/04091723/Ruff-Cycles-Biggie-e-bike_Bosch-mid-motor-cafe-racer-cruiser-with-bags-120x96.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/04091723/Ruff-Cycles-Biggie-e-bike_Bosch-mid-motor-cafe-racer-cruiser-with-bags-768x614.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1500px) 100vw, 1500px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb28 src ng ngcb28 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/04091723/Ruff-Cycles-Biggie-e-bike_Bosch-mid-motor-cafe-racer-cruiser-with-bags.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/04091723/Ruff-Cycles-Biggie-e-bike_Bosch-mid-motor-cafe-racer-cruiser-with-bags.jpg 1500w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/04091723/Ruff-Cycles-Biggie-e-bike_Bosch-mid-motor-cafe-racer-cruiser-with-bags-297x238.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/04091723/Ruff-Cycles-Biggie-e-bike_Bosch-mid-motor-cafe-racer-cruiser-with-bags-800x640.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/04091723/Ruff-Cycles-Biggie-e-bike_Bosch-mid-motor-cafe-racer-cruiser-with-bags-120x96.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/04091723/Ruff-Cycles-Biggie-e-bike_Bosch-mid-motor-cafe-racer-cruiser-with-bags-768x614.jpg 768w\"></a></p><p>A newer style of e-bike cruiser from Ruff is their new Biggie cafe racer. Pretty much a scaled-up version of their previous Lil’ Buddy, the new Biggies share a similar open loop style steel frame but much larger 26×3.0″ tires. Like the chopper, the Biggie is made in Europe and offered with tons of options for personalization.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/04091718/Ruff-Cycles-Biggie-e-bike_Bosch-mid-motor-cafe-racer-cruiser-frame-loop-detail.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/04091718/Ruff-Cycles-Biggie-e-bike_Bosch-mid-motor-cafe-racer-cruiser-frame-loop-detail.jpg\" alt=\"Ruff Cycles Biggie cafe racer e-bike cruiser detail\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1000\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/04091718/Ruff-Cycles-Biggie-e-bike_Bosch-mid-motor-cafe-racer-cruiser-frame-loop-detail.jpg 1500w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/04091718/Ruff-Cycles-Biggie-e-bike_Bosch-mid-motor-cafe-racer-cruiser-frame-loop-detail-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/04091718/Ruff-Cycles-Biggie-e-bike_Bosch-mid-motor-cafe-racer-cruiser-frame-loop-detail-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/04091718/Ruff-Cycles-Biggie-e-bike_Bosch-mid-motor-cafe-racer-cruiser-frame-loop-detail-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/04091718/Ruff-Cycles-Biggie-e-bike_Bosch-mid-motor-cafe-racer-cruiser-frame-loop-detail-768x512.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1500px) 100vw, 1500px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb28 src ng ngcb28 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/04091718/Ruff-Cycles-Biggie-e-bike_Bosch-mid-motor-cafe-racer-cruiser-frame-loop-detail.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/04091718/Ruff-Cycles-Biggie-e-bike_Bosch-mid-motor-cafe-racer-cruiser-frame-loop-detail.jpg 1500w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/04091718/Ruff-Cycles-Biggie-e-bike_Bosch-mid-motor-cafe-racer-cruiser-frame-loop-detail-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/04091718/Ruff-Cycles-Biggie-e-bike_Bosch-mid-motor-cafe-racer-cruiser-frame-loop-detail-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/04091718/Ruff-Cycles-Biggie-e-bike_Bosch-mid-motor-cafe-racer-cruiser-frame-loop-detail-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/04091718/Ruff-Cycles-Biggie-e-bike_Bosch-mid-motor-cafe-racer-cruiser-frame-loop-detail-768x512.jpg 768w\"></a></p><p>Buyers 